  "text": "The Parameter-less Evolutionary Portfolio (P-EP) implements a heuristic that performs adaptive selection of parameter-less evolutionary algorithms (P-EAs) in accordance with performance criteria that are measured during running time. This heuristic is inspired by the parameter-less genetic algorithm (P-GA) [CITATION_1] and was first proposed by [CITATION_2] . We direct the interested reader to these papers for a more general and detailed description of the heuristic itself.",
